title: Preseason Power-Up + Rankings Reactions, Megalabowl! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/22
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, a BIG announcement, and important takeaways from the preseason action! What’s the level of concern for Antonio Gibson? Is Devin Singletary the Bills RB to target in fantasy football drafts? Plus, the latest NFL News including updates for Michael Thomas and Tom Brady. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 22nd, 2022
